WEBVTT

00:00:22.200 --> 00:00:27.000
ARC SE asked what could survive.

00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:32.700
Every ecosystem needs observers.

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:39.700
Watcher was not only a concept. It had
an interface.

00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:46.700
Performance became memory.

00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:53.700
Collection became preservation.

00:00:55.900 --> 00:01:00.700
The observer left evidence behind.

00:01:02.900 --> 00:01:07.700
Every memory needs governance.

00:01:09.900 --> 00:01:14.700
Coordinator existed as a real command
boundary.

00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:22.700
Routing became inspectable.

00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:29.700
Every claim needs a body.

00:01:31.900 --> 00:01:36.700
Core held operational truth.

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:44.700
Execution was visible.

00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:51.700
Parity made it comparable.

00:01:53.900 --> 00:01:58.700
The bearish hunter had an identity.

00:02:00.900 --> 00:02:05.700
Then the real organism appeared.

00:02:08.900 --> 00:02:13.700
The evidence followed.

00:02:15.900 --> 00:02:20.700
The bullish hunter had an identity.

00:02:22.900 --> 00:02:27.700
Then the real organism appeared.

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:35.700
The evidence followed.

00:02:37.900 --> 00:02:42.700
Strike entered as the executor.

00:02:44.900 --> 00:02:49.700
The evidence surface was real.

00:02:51.900 --> 00:02:56.700
Micro Harvest entered as the
collector.

00:02:58.900 --> 00:03:03.700
Its real interface survived.

00:03:06.900 --> 00:03:11.700
Its evidence survived.

00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:18.700
And then the realization: this
actually existed.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:25.700
The organisms worked as a system.

00:03:27.900 --> 00:03:32.700
ARC SE. Request the evidence vault.

00:03:36.700 --> 00:03:39.250
This is not the destination.

00:03:39.500 --> 00:03:42.350
It is only the first generation.

00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:47.150
This is what we envision to become.
